iate from the otherwise-optimal myopic sensing\ngiven additional exploration opportunities, i.e., when $m<k$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2013 19:01:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-17"}
