te to decide a perfect matching with rectangles\nin the case where all points have the same color, solving an open problem of\nBereg, Mutsanas, and Wolff [CGTA (2009)].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2013 19:46:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Jan 2014 15:42:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-06"}
